 produce\nsuch Paramount releases as \u201cTop Gun: Maverick\u201d and \u201cMission: Impossible \u2013 Dead\nReckoning.\u201d\n\nEarlier this week, New York-based Paramount said that Bob Bakish would step\ndown as CEO of the film, television and multimedia company, to be replaced by\na troika of executives who will form a new \u201cOffice of the CEO.\u201d\n\nby Taboola by Taboola\n\nSuggested For You\n\nRemains of child found in duffel bag in Philadelphia neighborhood identified\nas missing boy\n\nUndo\n\nTreppenlift-VergleichAd Content\n\nAdvertisement Rentner in Riesa: So kosten Treppenlifte fast nichtsTreppenlift-\nVergleich:\n\nAdvertisement Advertisement\n\nUndo\n\n'What do we got to pay for this?' Jurors in Trump hush money trial hear\nrecording of pivotal call\n\nUndo\n\nArkansas governor says state won't comply with new federal rules on treatment\nof trans students\n\nUndo\n\nEmployer of visiting nurse who was killed didn't protect her and should be\nfined, safety agency says\n\nUndo\n\nFather of former youth detention center resident testifies against him in New\nHampshire trialThe father of a man who says he was raped and beaten as a teen\nat New Hampshire\u2019s youth detention center has testified that his son had a\nreputation for dishonesty.AP News\n\nUndo\n\nJudge grants autopsy rules requested by widow of Mississippi man found dead\nafter vanishingA Mississippi judge granted a request Thursday by the widow of\na deceased man who vanished under mysterious circumstances to set standards\nfor a future independent autopsy of her late husband\u2019s body.AP News\n\nUndo\n\nAd Content\n\nAdvertisement: Solar Vergleich\n\nRentner entdeckt \"Solar-Erfindung\" - Industrie sprachlosAdvertisement: Solar\nVergleich\n\nUndo\n\nAdvertisement: Treppenlift-Vergleich\n\nRiesa: So kosten Treppenlifte fast nichtsAdvertisement: Treppenlift-Vergleich\n\nUndo\n\nAdvertisement: Apotheken Magazin\n\nPrivatversicherte \u00fcber 55 Jahren k\u00f6nnen bis zu 70% sparenAdvert